HEADWORD: Lasiocampidae
<hw>Lasiocampidae</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A natural family of moths
whose larvae include the tent caterpillars; the eggars; the lappet
moths.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family <fam>Lasiocampidae</fam>.</syn>⟦br⟧
